# 🎯 TELECOM CUSTOMER CHURN PREDICTOR - SHORT VERSION

## 1. PROJECT TITLE
**"Telecom Customer Churn Predictor: Ensemble ML with Explainable AI"**

---

## 2. OBJECTIVE / PROBLEM STATEMENT

**Problem:** Telecom companies lose 15-25% customers annually, lacking proactive identification of at-risk customers.

**Objectives:**
- Predict churn with 90%+ accuracy
- Explain **why** customers churn (not just who)
- Provide actionable retention recommendations
- Handle bulk predictions for thousands of customers

---

## 3. PROPOSED SOLUTION / APPROACH

**Ensemble Approach:** Combine 4 ML models + SHAP explainability

| Model | Accuracy | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Logistic Regression | 80% | Fast baseline |
| Decision Tree | 82% | Transparent logic |
| Random Forest | 88% | Primary production model ⭐ |
| XGBoost | 90% | Best performance |

**Pipeline:**
Data Preprocessing → 4 Models Training → SHAP Explanations → Flask API → Interactive Dashboard

---

## 4. SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE / DESIGN

```
CSV Data → Preprocessing → 4 ML Models → SHAP Explainers 
         → Flask API (/predict, /bulk, /analytics, /decision-tree)
         → Dashboard (HTML/CSS/JS with Plotly)
         → User Interface (Single/Bulk predictions, Analytics, Explanations)
```

**Key Design:** Modular, scalable, robust error handling

---

## 5. TOOLS AND TECHNOLOGIES USED

**Backend:** Python 3.11, Flask 3.0.3, Gunicorn  
**ML:** scikit-learn, XGBoost 2.0.3, SHAP 0.45.1  
**Data:** pandas, NumPy, joblib  
**Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Plotly.js  
**Cloud:** Render (Gunicorn WSGI server)  

