## 8. CHALLENGES FACED

| Challenge | Solution |
|---|---|
| Model accuracy vs. explainability | Ensemble: RF (88%) for production, XGBoost (90%) for backup, DT for transparency |
| SHAP memory usage (500MB+) | Pre-load explainers at startup; use --preload in Gunicorn |
| Variable CSV formats | Flexible column mapping with fallback checks |
| Slow SHAP computation (2-3s) | Pre-computed explainers; optimized pipeline; response time <500ms |
| Data quality issues | Robust preprocessing: missing value handling, type conversion |
| Large dataset rendering | Pagination, lazy loading, Plotly optimization |

